\c 15
\s Munhu angagara mutende raJehovha?
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha, ndiani achagara mutende renyu\x + Map. 24.3,4. Isa. 33.16.\x*? Ndiani angagara pagomo renyu dzvene\x + Map. 2.6.\x*?
\v 2 Uyo anofamba asina mhosva\x + Isa. 33.15.\x*, uye anoita zvakarurama\x + Map. 106.3.\x*, uye anotaura chokwadi mumoyo make\x + Zek. 8.16. VaEfe. 4.25. Joh. 1.47. VaKoro. 3.9.\x*.
\v 3 Iye asingatauri\x + Rev. 19.16. Map. 34.13.\x* makuhwa nerurimi rwake\x + 2 Sam. 19.27.\x*, asingaitiri shamwari yake zvakaipa, uye asingasimudziri kutuka kune wekwake.
\v 4 Wakarashwa anomhurwa pameso ake, asi anoremekedza vanotya Jehovha; anopikira zvinokuvadza, asi haashanduki.
\v 5 Asingapi mari yake nemubereko\x + Eki. 22.25.\x*, uye asingagamuchiri fufuro pane asina mhosva\x + Eki. 23.8.\x*. Anoita izvi haazungunuswi kusvika rinhi\x + Map. 10.6.\x*.